when you were young?

137
00:06:48,175 --> 00:06:50,480
You shut your phone and went back home.

138
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,880
You even left a note.

139
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,920
Now you want to eat!

140
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:54,525
