242
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:31,900
Um.

243
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:09,400
Dad.

244
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,275
Gu Xiao, you're back.

245
00:16:50,575 --> 00:16:52,479
It's too depressing in their family.

246
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,520
