267
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:33,040
Boring?

268
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,520
Then tell me what you can do.

269
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:36,319
I don't know.

270
00:17:36,575 --> 00:17:37,520
I have no idea.

271
00:17:38,175 --> 00:17:39,725
